---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="1. Strategic Premise">
    <!-- The Personal Premise -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-pistos-black mb-6 leading-tight">
            An Ecosystem for <span class="text-pistos-red">Serious Entrepreneurs.</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="bg-pistos-surface border border-pistos-border p-8 rounded border-l-4 border-l-pistos-black shadow-sm space-y-6">
            <div>
                <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black mb-2">1. Strategic Direction</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted">
                    Following a conversation with Mr. Shabib regarding his vision for Pistos and his existing portfolio, the strategic direction is clear. The goal is <strong>not</strong> to compete with the 200+ agencies in Dubai that compete primarily on price. Pistos is positioned to serve serious entrepreneurs looking for reliable, long-term operational infrastructure — not just a trade license.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-pistos-border pt-6">
                <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold text-pistos-black mb-2">2. The Ecosystem Advantage</h2>
                <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-pistos-muted mb-4">
                    Pistos does not stand alone; it acts as the primary acquisition funnel for Mr. Shabib’s wider ecosystem. The true business model lies in cross-pollination. Pistos captures the client at genesis, and seamlessly feeds them into:
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 font-mono text-sm text-pistos-black">
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="calculator" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">The One Accountant</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Tax & Audit Services</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="building" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">DuneSaura</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">Real Estate & Workspaces</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-pistos-border rounded p-4 flex flex-col items-start space-y-2 bg-pistos-bg hover:border-pistos-black transition-colors">
                        <i data-lucide="monitor-stop" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold">Mindcom</span>
                        <span class="text-xs text-pistos-muted">IT & Microsoft Cloud Solutions</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- The Architectural Crisis (Dramatic Redesign) -->
            <div class="mt-20 pt-16 border-t-2 border-pistos-black" data-aos="fade-up">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center mb-12">
                    <i data-lucide="split" class="w-12 h-12 text-pistos-red mb-4"></i>
                    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-pistos-black uppercase tracking-tight">Website Direction</h2>
                    <p class="text-xl text-pistos-muted mt-4 max-w-2xl">There are two common approaches in this market. The choice shapes the entire digital infrastructure.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-pistos-border overflow-hidden rounded-lg shadow-xl" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                    
                    <!-- Option A: Absher -->
                    <div class="bg-pistos-black text-white p-10 md:p-14 group hover:bg-[#111] transition-colors relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity transform group-hover:scale-110">
                            <i data-lucide="crosshairs" class="w-48 h-48 text-white"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8 border-b border-white/20 pb-4">
                                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-red tracking-widest uppercase">Option A</span>
                                <span class="text-xs bg-pistos-red text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-mono font-bold">Focused</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Setup-Focused Website</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                                A focused portal that leads with Business Setup only. Other services (Tax, IT, Real Estate) are introduced after the client is onboarded. Modeled after the <strong>DUQE</strong> conversion approach.
                            </p>
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
                                    <i data-lucide="zap" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                                    <span>Higher conversion for setup-related leads.</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
                                    <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                                    <span>The full scope of the ecosystem is not immediately visible.</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Option B: HLB -->
                    <div class="bg-white text-pistos-black p-10 md:p-14 group hover:bg-[#f8f8f8] transition-colors relative overflow-hidden">
                        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-5 group-hover:opacity-10 transition-opacity transform group-hover:scale-110">
                            <i data-lucide="landmark" class="w-48 h-48 text-pistos-black"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative z-10">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8 border-b border-pistos-border pb-4">
                                <span class="text-xs font-mono text-pistos-muted tracking-widest uppercase">Option B</span>
                                <span class="text-xs bg-pistos-black text-white px-3 py-1 rounded font-mono font-bold">Comprehensive</span>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Full Ecosystem Website</h3>
                            <p class="text-pistos-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
                                A broad corporate site that presents all services equally on the homepage. Modeled after the <strong>HLB HAMT</strong> approach. Communicates scale and range, but can create decision fatigue for first-time visitors.
                            </p>
                            <div class="space-y-3">
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm text-pistos-muted">
                                    <i data-lucide="shield" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-black shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                                    <span>Communicates credibility and institutional size.</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 text-sm text-pistos-muted">
                                    <i data-lucide="alert-triangle" class="w-5 h-5 text-pistos-red shrink-0 mt-0.5"></i>
                                    <span>Can overwhelm visitors looking for a straightforward setup.</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                
                <!-- The Verdict -->
                <div class="mt-12 bg-pistos-red text-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-2xl relative overflow-hidden" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/10"></div>
                    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:items-start space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-6">
                        <i data-lucide="check-circle-2" class="w-12 h-12 text-white/90 shrink-0"></i>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl mb-2">Recommendation: A Hybrid Approach</h4>
                            <p class="text-white/90 leading-relaxed text-lg font-medium">
                                The public-facing website focuses on Business Setup to keep the message clear and the conversion path simple. Once a client enters the private portal (Layer 2), the full ecosystem — Tax, IT, Real Estate — is presented in context, where it is more relevant and actionable.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-2xl font-heading mt-16 mb-8 text-center text-pistos-black leading-relaxed italic border-t border-b border-pistos-border py-8">
            "A digital presence that reflects the seriousness<br>and operational depth of the business."
        </p>

        <div class="flex justify-end mt-12 mb-32">
            <a href="/" class="group flex items-center space-x-2 text-pistos-muted hover:text-pistos-black font-medium transition-colors">
                <i data-lucide="arrow-left" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
                <span>Summary</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/competitors" class="group flex items-center space-x-2 text-pistos-red hover:text-[#852326] font-medium transition-colors">
                <span>Next: 2. Market Benchmarks</span>
                <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4 transform group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"></i>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
